reviewText: Sure this has nudity, but there are other places you can find better nudity.  This movie is one I vaguely remember watching when I was younger and I bought it thinking it would be good.  No, I guess I focused on the nudity that I forgot what a dumb plot there was and how short the nude scenes were.  You can get better nude scenes for cheaper.  This is just a 90's pay per view movie that shouldn't even be remembered.
